{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"URL.createObjectURL()","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URL/createObjectURl","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL_API\">URL API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URL\"><code>URL</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Construtor</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/URL\"><code>URL()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propriedades</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/hash\"><code>hash</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/host\"><code>host</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/hostname\"><code>hostname</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/href\"><code>href</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/origin\"><code>origin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/password\"><code>password</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/pathname\"><code>pathname</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/port\"><code>port</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/protocol\"><code>protocol</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/search\"><code>search</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URL/searchParams\"><code>searchParams</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/username\"><code>username</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URL/createObjectURl\"><code>createObjectURL()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URL/revokeObjectURL\"><code>revokeObjectURL()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/toJSON\"><code>toJSON()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/toString\"><code>toString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a URL API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams\"><code>URLSearchParams</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>Esta é uma <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tecnologia experimental (en-US)</a></strong><br>Verifique a <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">tabela de compatibilidade entre Navegadores</a> cuidadosamente antes de usar essa funcionalidade em produção.</p></div><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"Resumo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Cria um novo objeto URL, cujo tempo de vida está ligado ao <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>document</code></a> na janela na qual este objeto foi criado. O novo objeto URL representa o objeto <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a> ou o objeto <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> passado como argumento.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>objetoURL</em> = window.URL.createObjectURL(blob);\n</pre>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code>blob</code> é um objeto do tipo <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a> ou <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> para o qual se deseja criar um objeto URL.</li>\n <li><code>objetoURL</code> é o objeto URL gerado. O conteúdo completo do arquivo especificado é representado pelo texto do objeto URL.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Veja <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/File_API/Using_files_from_web_applications#example.3a_using_object_urls_to_display_images\" title=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en/Using_files_from_web_applications#Example:_Using_object_URLs_to_display_images\">Using object URLs to display images</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"Notas","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Cada vez que a função <code>createObjectURL()</code> é chamada, um novo objeto URL é criado, mesmo se você já tiver criado um objeto URL para esse mesmo arquivo. Cada objeto URL criado precisa ser liberado por meio de uma chamada a <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/revokeObjectURL\"><code>window.URL.revokeObjectURL()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> quando este não for mais necessário. Os navegadores liberarão os objetos URL criados automaticamente quando o documento for descarregado; no entanto, para um desempenho e um gerenciamento de memória ótimos, se houver algum momento em que você puder liberar estes recursos explicitamente, você deveria fazê-lo.</p>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidade de navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.URL.createObjectURL","dataURL":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URL/createObjectURl/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URL/revokeObjectURL\"><code>URL.revokeObjectURL()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/File_API/Using_files_from_web_applications\" title=\"Using files from web applications\">Using files from web applications</a></li>\n <li>Especificação <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/FileAPI/#dfn-createObjectURL\" rel=\" noopener\">File API</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Resumo","id":"summary"},{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"example"},{"text":"Notas","id":"notes"},{"text":"Compatibilidade de navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Cria um novo objeto URL, cujo tempo de vida está ligado ao document na janela na qual este objeto foi criado. O novo objeto URL representa o objeto File ou o objeto Blob passado como argumento.","popularity":0.0005,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"URL.createObjectURL()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"URL.createObjectURL()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"URL.createObjectURL()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"URL.createObjectURL","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"URL.createObjectURL()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"URL.createObjectURL()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"URL.createObjectURL()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"URL.createObjectURL()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"URL.createObjectURL()","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/url/createobjecturl","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/url/createobjecturl/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URL","title":"URL"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URL/createObjectURl","title":"URL.createObjectURL()"}],"pageTitle":"URL.createObjectURL() - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}